result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both Cause Injury/Operate While und.Influence (1st) (PAC>=0.15) [Modifiers: Penalty-Intox. Operation of Motor Vehicle] and Cause Injury while Operating with PAC (1st)(PAC>=0.15) [Modifiers: Penalty-Intox. Operation of Motor Vehicle]. The defendant was found guilty of Cause Injury/Operate While und.Influence (1st) (PAC>=0.15) [Modifiers: Penalty-Intox. Operation of Motor Vehicle] and the other charge, Cause Injury while Operating with PAC (1st)(PAC>=0.15) [Modifiers: Penalty-Intox. Operation of Motor Vehicle] was dismissed by the court.

  • Trenton J Parker was found guilty of Injury by Intoxicated Use/Vehicle, a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.25(1)(a).
  • Trenton J Parker was found guilty of Cause Injury/Operate While und.Influence (1st) (PAC>=0.15) [Modifiers: Penalty-Intox. Operation of Motor Vehicle], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(2)(a)1.
